<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <class>AStringBuf</class>
    <method> Substring </method>

    <description>
        <para> 从此对象检索子字符串。子字符串从指定的字符位置开始。</para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> AString </return_val>
        <parameters>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>Int32</param_type>
            <param_name> start </param_name>
            <param_note>
                <para> 开始位置 </para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>AStringBuf &amp;</param_type>
            <param_name> sub </param_name>
            <param_note>
                <para>保存子字符串的AStringBuf对象 </para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>Encoding</param_type>
            <param_name>encoding</param_name>
            <param_default> Encoding_Default</param_default>
            <param_note>
                <para> 指定编码格式。参见<link url="../../../others/Encoding.htm">Encoding</link>枚举类型说明。</para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>                  
        </parameters>        
    </syntax>
    <return>
        <para>返回子字符串。如果源对象包含的字符串指针为NULL或sub AStringBuf对象的m_pBuf指针为NULL， start 小于0 或大于源字符串的长度， 返回的AStringBuf对象包含的字符串指针指向NULL。</para>
    </return>
<example>
<pre>
AStringBuf_&lt;20&gt; asbuf;
AStringBuf_&lt;20&gt; assub;
asbuf.Copy("123456789");  
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf);  //Display : "123456789"
CConsole::WriteLine(asbuf.Substring(2,assub));  //Display : "3456789"
CConsole::WriteLine(assub);  //Display : "3456789"
</pre>
</example> 
 
